reviews.text:
Very good value noodle dishes in a cool environment. The staff is friendly and there is also a English menue in case you can't decide what you want to eat from the pictures. You have the option to pick from various noodle styles and spicylevels.

I recommend getting a bowl with meatballs. Those are absolutely delicious. There are also various breakfast dishes which are very good as well. Recommending this place!

result.name: 港灣豪庭廣場

reviews.text: 不太多選擇❗
自從千色店只剩下二樓一層之後，地下一層感覺相當冷清，加上千色店及一般商舖營業時間只到晚上9點，所以晚上9點後人流明顯減少很多！
這個廣場好像是為維港灣豪庭住客設計。有櫃員機，地方闊落，酒家食肆，樣樣有，還有很多小朋友，唔係好逼，舒服。
千色店沒前大；縮了地下那層，只有上層很快便逛畢
地方尚算雅潔，食肆及售賣的東西也不少。
